citRespParty.rpOrgName: Papua New Guinea National Statistics Office

idCitation.resTitle: PAPUA NEW GUINEA: Admin Level 3 Boundaries

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This spatial dataset provides the delimitation and composition of the Papua New Guinea administrative level 3 (local government area) boundary polygons.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataIdInfo.idPurp: Administrative Level 3 Boundaries of Papua New Guinea
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This dataset was provided to the UN-OCHA Regional Office for the Asia-Pacific by the National Statistics Office.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Fixed double space errors in Admin3 names "Unggai Rural LLG" and "Gama Rural LLG". 2. Fixed multipart slivers in Admin3 "Bamu Rural LLG", "Tinputz LLG", "Upper/Lower Koronigl LLG", "Rabaul Urban LLG", "Inland Baining Rural LLG", "East Pomio Rural LLG", "Namatanai Rural LLG", "Central Kerema Rural LLG", "Baimuru Rural LLG", "East Kikori Rural LLG" and "West Kikori Rural LLG". 3. Fixed gap error for "East Kerema Rural LLG" with bordering unit "Lakekamu-Tauri Rural LLG".
The following was found by ITOS but is not addressed in this version: 1.The slashes and parentheses in some names suggest the presence of alternate names that should be separated and placed in AltName fields. 2. Admin3 "Goroka Urban LLG", "Kiwai Rural LLG", "Gogodala Rural LLG" and "Kainantu Urban LLG" have multipart polygons that may be errors.
